'''MSQWL700GE''' would not seem to be a valid FCC ID.
The default SSID may be '''WL700gE-''' followed by 4 upper or lower-case letters.
There is a '''VIA''' VT6212L USB 2.0 controller on-board. There is also a '''ACARD''' ATP865-B on board for the 3.5" IDE interface.
==Additional external links== *[http://wiki.openwrt.org/oldwiki/openwrtdocs/hardware/asus/wl700ge On the '''OpenWrt''' Wiki] *[http://www.sukkamehulinko.romikselle.com/wl700g/ Internal shots] ([http://web.archive.org/web/20090402002256/http://www.sukkamehulinko.romikselle.com/wl700g/ via archive.org]) :"WL-700GE_R1.14" and the '''ASUS''' logo is silkscreened on the board shown.
